Description.LocalizedString: A dangerous and terrifying warrior obsessed with death and darkness.
Shining cold iron adorned his body from head to toe, making him an unstoppable juggernaut.
A massive weapon capable of cleaving a foe in half, in the right hands.
A deadly and blood-soaked warrior obsessed with death and darkness.
Bloody cold iron adorned his body from head to toe, making him a terrifying juggernaut.
A massive and gory weapon that cleaved many a foe in half.
Valuing research over violence, he took to studying the ancient and esoteric.
After what felt like lifetimes travelling through Lost Realms, he found this jacket to protect him from the harsh environment.
These modern jeans were well suited to the Trials.
